subject: Rogers Cup (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Goffin, seeded 13th, topped Steve Johnson, 6-2, 6-2, and the 14th-seeded Dimitrov downed Alexandr Dolgopolov, 6-4, 7-5 in the second round of the Rogers Cup
